<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 09:12:20 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国煤炭集团表示，美国对俄罗斯的限制是为了保持高价格，损害了出口</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-coal-group-says-us-curbs-russia-keep-prices-high-hurt-exports-2024-03-13/</link><description>中国一个行业组织周三警告称，美国对俄罗斯煤炭公司更严厉的制裁将在短期内使全球高热值煤炭价格保持在高位，影响俄罗斯五分之一的煤炭出口。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 08:57:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-coal-group-says-us-curbs-russia-keep-prices-high-hurt-exports-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>阿迪达斯 30 年来首次亏损，但仍坚持派息</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/adidas-warns-2024-sales-decline-over-stocked-north-america-market-2024-03-13/</link><description>德国运动服装巨头阿迪达斯周三公布了 2023 年 30 多年来的首次亏损，首席执行官比约恩·古尔登 (Bjorn Gulden) 在与说唱歌手坎耶·韦斯特 (Kanye West) 分手后，致力于扭转该品牌的局面。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 06:34:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/adidas-warns-2024-sales-decline-over-stocked-north-america-market-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>抵押贷款违约率上升给中国家庭带来更多痛苦</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/rising-mortgage-defaults-bring-more-pain-chinese-households-2024-03-13/</link><description>在中国南方城市，前金融工作者雷晓宇因抵押贷款拖欠而被收债人追捕，她不再接听电话，试图推迟不可避免的事情。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 06:06:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/rising-mortgage-defaults-bring-more-pain-chinese-households-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>随着对华贸易的蓬勃发展，一些俄罗斯企业蓬勃发展</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/trade-with-china-booms-some-russian-companies-are-flourishing-2024-03-13/</link><description>尼基塔·米年科夫 (Nikita Minenkov) 的物流公司位于俄罗斯和中国边界的阿穆尔河附近，业务进展顺利。自从莫斯科入侵乌克兰以来，情况变得更好——公司营业额连续两年翻了一番。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 06:03:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/trade-with-china-booms-some-russian-companies-are-flourishing-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>河北省发生特大爆炸，造成2人死亡26人受伤</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/explosion-hebei-china-restaurant-injures-several-people-state-media-reports-2024-03-13/</link><description>官方媒体和当局周三表示，中国北部省份河北省一家餐馆疑似煤气泄漏，引发爆炸，建筑物外墙被撕裂，汽车受损，碎片散落，造成两人死亡、26 人受伤。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 02:42:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/explosion-hebei-china-restaurant-injures-several-people-state-media-reports-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>中国电动汽车巨头比亚迪推出新版e2掀背车，起售价更低</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-ev-giant-byd-launches-new-version-e2-hatchback-with-lower-starting-price-2024-03-13/</link><description>中国电动汽车巨头比亚迪周三推出了新版 e2 EV 掀背车，起价低于其前身。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 01:39:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-ev-giant-byd-launches-new-version-e2-hatchback-with-lower-starting-price-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>随着财政紧缩，中国孩子的体育和音乐课程急剧减少</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/sports-music-lessons-chinas-kids-sharp-decline-purse-strings-tighten-2024-03-13/</link><description>去年8月，张兆琳在一家中国互联网公司被解雇后，就让她10岁的儿子退出了他喜欢的足球班。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 01:13:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/sports-music-lessons-chinas-kids-sharp-decline-purse-strings-tighten-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>据新闻网站报道，碧桂园境内债券持有人尚未收到息票付款</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/country-garden-onshore-bondholders-have-not-received-coupon-payment-news-site-2024-03-13/</link><description>据中国数字新闻媒体澎湃新闻报道，碧桂园的境内债券持有人表示，他们尚未收到周二到期的息票付款。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 01:07:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/country-garden-onshore-bondholders-have-not-received-coupon-payment-news-site-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>2月份全球电动汽车销量因中国新年庆祝活动受损</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/global-electric-car-sales-february-hurt-by-chinas-new-year-celebrations-2024-03-13/</link><description>市场研究公司 Rho Motion 表示，2 月份全球纯电动和插电式混合动力汽车 (PHEV) 销量较去年同期微幅增长 3%，主要是受中国农历新年庆祝活动的影响。周三。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 00:03:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/global-electric-car-sales-february-hurt-by-chinas-new-year-celebrations-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>美国众议院将就 TikTok 打击行动进行投票；参议院命运未卜</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-house-vote-tiktok-crackdown-fate-uncertain-senate-2024-03-12/</link><description>美国众议院计划周三对一项法案进行投票，该法案将给 TikTok 的中国所有者字节跳动大约六个月的时间剥离这款约 1.7 亿美国人使用的短视频应用程序，否则将面临禁令。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 23:25:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-house-vote-tiktok-crackdown-fate-uncertain-senate-2024-03-12/</guid></item><item><title>日本太空一号公司的 Kairos 火箭在首次飞行时爆炸</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/japans-space-one-counts-down-inaugural-kairos-rocket-launch-2024-03-12/</link><description>Kairos 是日本太空一号制造的小型固体燃料火箭，周三首次发射后几秒钟就发生爆炸，该公司试图成为第一家将卫星送入轨道的日本公司。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 23:12:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/japans-space-one-counts-down-inaugural-kairos-rocket-launch-2024-03-12/</guid></item><item><title>芒果适应气候变化使时尚不再季节性</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/mango-adapts-climate-change-makes-fashion-less-seasonal-2024-03-12/</link><description>西班牙零售商Mango首席执行官托尼·鲁伊斯(Toni Ruiz)告诉路透社，由于气候变化使时尚不再那么季节性，西班牙零售商Mango正在研发适应性强的服装，以帮助顾客适应气温的剧烈波动。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 23:03:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/mango-adapts-climate-change-makes-fashion-less-seasonal-2024-03-12/</guid></item><item><title>美国众议院共和党人不顾特朗普的反对，继续推进 TikTok 法案</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-house-republicans-forge-ahead-with-tiktok-bill-despite-trump-2024-03-12/</link><description>美国众议院共和党人周二誓言要继续投票禁止流行的 TikTok 社交媒体应用程序，尽管唐纳德·特朗普对众议院微弱多数席位拥有巨大影响力，但他对此表示担忧。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 20:50:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-house-republicans-forge-ahead-with-tiktok-bill-despite-trump-2024-03-12/</guid></item><item><title>特斯拉官员谈东南亚扩张 中国比亚迪领先</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-official-talks-up-southeast-asia-expansion-chinas-byd-pulls-ahead-2024-03-12/</link><description>特斯拉一位高管周二表示，进军东南亚是该公司的首要任务，突显了该美国电动汽车制造商面临来自中国比亚迪的竞争的快速增长市场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 18:12:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-official-talks-up-southeast-asia-expansion-chinas-byd-pulls-ahead-2024-03-12/</guid></item><item><title>美国间谍头子“不能排除”中国将利用TikTok影响美国大选</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-spy-chief-cannot-rule-out-that-china-would-use-tiktok-influence-us-elections-2024-03-12/</link><description>美国国家情报总监艾薇儿·海恩斯 (Avril Haines) 周二在众议院情报委员会听证会上表示，中国可能利用社交媒体应用 TikTok 影响 2024 年美国大选。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 16:27:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-spy-chief-cannot-rule-out-that-china-would-use-tiktok-influence-us-elections-2024-03-12/</guid></item></channel></rss>